Class WebSocketFrameDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
      • org.jboss.netty.handler.codec.frame.FrameDecoder
        • org.jboss.netty.handler.codec.replay.ReplayingDecoder<VoidEnum>
          • org.jboss.netty.handler.codec.http.websocket.WebSocketFrameDecoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChannelHandler, ChannelUpstreamHandler, LifeCycleAwareChannelHandler
    Deprecated. 
    Use org.jboss.netty.handler.codec.http.websocketx instead. Decodes ChannelBuffers into WebSocketFrames.

    For the detailed instruction on adding add Web Socket support to your HTTP server, take a look into the WebSocketServer example located in the org.jboss.netty.example.http.websocket package.
